The fix is in place and correctly formatted. Here is a summary of what was done.

**File edited:** `/Users/thamsanqamoyo/Documents/code/jem-open/jem-sec-attest/app/[tenant]/training/page.tsx`

**Change (lines 670-674):**

Before:
```typescript
if (!res.ok) return;
```

After:
```typescript
if (!res.ok) {
